title: Are Rita Ora, Travis Barker `seriously` dating?
text:

Washington D.C., Oct 1 (ANI): Rita Ora has found love again after long-time in musician Travis Barker, as she has been repeatedly spotted getting cozy with the drummer since meeting him at the Power 106 All-Star Game in Los Angeles. A source close to the music artists informed that the 'I Will Never Let You Down' hit-maker and the Blink-182 frontman have been together ever since the All-Star Game and are very much into each other, Us Magazine reported. The source added that the 39-year-old American drummer finds the singer interesting and beautiful. Barker, who was married to Shanna Moakler from 2004 to 2009, was previously linked to UFC ring girl Arianny Celeste, whereas Ora recently split from her boyfriend of over a year, Tommy Hilfiger's son Ricky.
